                "invention-title": [
                    "System and method for simultaneously producing low-carbon pure iron, vanadyl sulfate, titanium dioxide and high-end sponge titanium from sefstromite",
                    "一种钒钛铁矿同时生产低碳纯铁、硫酸氧钒、钛白粉和高端海绵钛的系统及方法"
                ]
            },
            "abstract": [
                {
                    "p": "The invention belongs to the field of energy and metallurgy. Specifically, the invention discloses a system and a method for simultaneously producing low-carbon pure iron, vanadyl sulfate, titanium dioxide and high-end sponge titanium from sefstromite. The sefstromite is subjected to direct acidolysis through the acidolysis separation procedure, and vanadyl sulfate, titanyl sulfate and ferric salt crystals are separated. The titanyl sulfate is subjected to fine particle hydrolysis to produce the sulfuric acid method titanium dioxide. The high-end sponge titanium is prepared from titanyl sulfate through coarse grain hydrolysis, fluidized calcination, fluidized chlorination and magnesiothermic reduction. The ferric salt is subjected to dissolution and purification to obtain a ferric salt solution, dissolved slag and purified slag. And resource utilization and sulfur circulation of the dissolving slag and the purifying slag are realized through high-temperature desulfurization. Pure iron preparation, sulfuric acid circulation and recycling of hydrogen and oxygen are realized through valence state adjustment and battery ironmaking procedures. And the solar furnace is used for supplying heat to high-temperature desulfurization and acidolysis procedures, so that low carbonization of energy is realized. The method is suitable for large-scale and continuous treatment of the sefstromite, and has the advantages of high efficiency, low energy consumption, no pollution, good economical efficiency and the like."
                },
                {
                    "p": "本发明属于能源、冶金领域。具体地，本发明公开了一种钒钛铁矿同时生产低碳纯铁、硫酸氧钒、钛白粉和高端海绵钛的系统及方法。通过酸解分离工序对钒钛铁矿进行直接酸解，分离硫酸氧钒、硫酸氧钛及铁盐晶体。硫酸氧钛通过细粒水解生产硫酸法钛白粉。硫酸氧钛通过粗粒水解、流态化煅烧、流态化氯化、镁热还原制备高端海绵钛。铁盐通过溶解净化工序，得到铁盐溶液、溶解渣和净化渣。通过高温脱硫实现溶解渣和净化渣的资源化利用和硫循环。通过价态调整、电池炼铁工序实现纯铁制备，硫酸循环和氢气、氧气的回收利用。通过太阳能炉为高温脱硫和酸解工序供热，实现能源低碳化。本发明适用于大规模、连续化处理钒钛铁矿，具有效率高、能耗低、无污染和经济性好等优点。"
                }
